channel.title: Is your problem this? Ask yourself
channel.description:
[b]If something on your server isn't going in the order it's supposed to, it's not doing anything at all when you have the code compiled for it, then there really is nothing [u]we[/u] can do for you.[/b]
[i]Java's DatagramPackets do not guarantee proper delivery order or even delivery. If you have one of the problems above, work on getting a better internet connection and it will resolve it. Having too many people online for your connection may also cause the problem above.[/i]
Thanks.
